Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.86,English,,0,0,0,,- Alright, I'm about to go for my first ever ride in a fully autonomous vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.62,English,,0,0,0,,Whoa, no driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:14.89,English,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:14.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.18,English,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Derek.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.16,English,,0,0,0,,This car is all yours with no one up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.73,English,,0,0,0,,- I really like the idea of fully autonomous vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:26.76,English,,0,0,0,,but it's weird getting into a car with no driver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:26.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.40,English,,0,0,0,,and just trusting the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.25,English,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna report back how this ride goes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:33.49,English,,0,0,0,,and how I feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:33.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.66,English,,0,0,0,,Oh, but full disclosure, this video is sponsored by Waymo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:45.01,English,,0,0,0,,Start ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:45.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.30,English,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:49.17,English,,0,0,0,,Make sure your seatbelt is fastened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:49.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:53.90,English,,0,0,0,,For any questions, press the Help button to speak with a rider support agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:53.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:54.92,English,,0,0,0,,- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:54.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.62,English,,0,0,0,,Now let's see where we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:59.50,English,,0,0,0,,It's looking at this car coming here. What's it gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:59.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.00,English,,0,0,0,,Oh, and it pulls in very smoothly behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.40,English,,0,0,0,,No problems. Did not turn into traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.68,English,,0,0,0,,Waited until the car has went, and then it turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.06,English,,0,0,0,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:14.28,English,,0,0,0,,I polled YouTube viewers about autonomous vehicles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:14.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:18.49,English,,0,0,0,,and half of you are excited and ready for them to be on the roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:18.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:24.01,English,,0,0,0,,but over 40% said you thought the technology was still over 10 years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:24.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:26.97,English,,0,0,0,,And for those people, I have news,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:26.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:30.40,English,,0,0,0,,which is that, well, there is no driver in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:30.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:34.17,English,,0,0,0,,I'm currently inside a fully autonomous vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:34.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.93,English,,0,0,0,,driving around a suburb of Phoenix, Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.93,English,,0,0,0,,Now I get that in some parts of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:42.02,English,,0,0,0,,like, the roads aren't well enough maintained
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:42.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.66,English,,0,0,0,,and people don't stay in their lane necessarily,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.89,English,,0,0,0,,and so it'd be very hard for a computer to drive there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:51.50,English,,0,0,0,,but at least under good conditions, the technology is currently functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:51.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:02.50,English,,0,0,0,,- Now Waymo started out as the Google self-driving car project
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:02.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:06.04,English,,0,0,0,,with what is possibly one of the cutest cars ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:06.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.78,English,,0,0,0,,I am inside the world's first fully autonomous vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.77,English,,0,0,0,,Back in October 2015, this car went on a public road,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:22.21,English,,0,0,0,,ridden by Steve Mann, who has a disability, he is legally blind,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:22.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:28.58,English,,0,0,0,,but he could get around in this thing, which is affectionately known as the Firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:28.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:32.32,English,,0,0,0,,This is such a simple vehicle. There's basically nothing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:32.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.64,English,,0,0,0,,There's no steering wheel, no dashboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.17,English,,0,0,0,,This car is super basic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.81,English,,0,0,0,,There is no AC,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:40.69,English,,0,0,0,,but there is an emergency stop button.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:40.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.10,English,,0,0,0,,That's my favorite button in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.72,English,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:48.73,English,,0,0,0,,You know, one of the important measures that they had to put in automatic elevators
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:48.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.10,English,,0,0,0,,was a big red stop button.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:56.06,English,,0,0,0,,Did you know that before the 1940s, almost all elevators had drivers in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:56.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.94,English,,0,0,0,,And when people started putting in driverless elevators,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.89,English,,0,0,0,,well, the public was very concerned, and they didn't wanna ride in those elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:08.92,English,,0,0,0,,There was one guy who was like, "I don't care if I have to walk up 12 flights of stairs for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:08.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.52,English,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking that elevator."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.57,English,,0,0,0,,And adoption was slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.39,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, they tried to advertise to help people understand that it was in fact safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:19.84,English,,0,0,0,,but, ultimately, there was an elevator drivers strike in New York City,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:19.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:24.99,English,,0,0,0,,and that really annoyed people, and it helped the adoption of automated elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:24.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.38,English,,0,0,0,,If you found a driver in an elevator today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.71,English,,0,0,0,,you would wonder, "Why are they there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.64,English,,0,0,0,,Now you might think an elevator is just so simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:35.45,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, it is effectively one dimensional motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:35.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:40.30,English,,0,0,0,,but airplanes are also flown extensively by computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:40.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:47.15,English,,0,0,0,,I saw this particular landing where a plane is coming in into Vienna,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:47.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:50.37,English,,0,0,0,,and it's just so foggy that the pilots can see almost nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:50.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.63,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is the view from the cockpit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:57.83,English,,0,0,0,,and yet, they make a perfect, a textbook landing right on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:57.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.67,English,,0,0,0,,So how do they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.04,English,,0,0,0,,The answer is the pilots didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.85,English,,0,0,0,,It was a CAT III autoland procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:10.03,English,,0,0,0,,The plane just came in and landed itself essentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:10.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:15.51,English,,0,0,0,,Now, of course, the pilots are important and they're monitoring all of the instruments and controls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:15.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:19.78,English,,0,0,0,,but it's actually the plane and its computer getting the plane to land appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:19.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:28.03,English,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to learn that humans are much more likely to take manual control and land on sunny days,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:28.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.13,English,,0,0,0,,like July 6th, 2013,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:34.95,English,,0,0,0,,when Asiana Airlines flight 214 was on final approach to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:34.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:40.55,English,,0,0,0,,Attempting to manually land the plane, the pilot accidentally left the throttle at zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:40.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.52,English,,0,0,0,,and by the time they realized and tried to abort the landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.09,English,,0,0,0,,it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:50.43,English,,0,0,0,,The plane crashed into the runway seawall and split in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:50.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.33,English,,0,0,0,,Three people died in the aftermath of this accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:05:02.44,English,,0,0,0,,I think the counterintuitive thing is that we expect the humans to be better, particularly in tough situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:05:02.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:08.32,English,,0,0,0,,but when it comes to airplanes, if it's bad weather, you actually want the plane flying itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:08.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.62,English,,0,0,0,,So the obvious next question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.78,English,,0,0,0,,would you want the same thing for cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:19.32,English,,0,0,0,,There are all these different levels of autonomy, and everything up to four
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:19.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:24.28,English,,0,0,0,,requires a human driver to be responsible and at the wheel at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:24.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.78,English,,0,0,0,,In the early days of the Google self-driving car project,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.52,English,,0,0,0,,they had a vehicle that was not yet level four,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.60,English,,0,0,0,,so it still required a human driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.24,English,,0,0,0,,They let Google employees borrow the cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.48,English,,0,0,0,,but they still had to be in control of the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:41.17,English,,0,0,0,,And the volunteers were informed that they were responsible for the car at all times
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:41.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.63,English,,0,0,0,,and that they would be constantly recorded, like video recorded, while they were in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:51.10,English,,0,0,0,,But still, within a short period of time, the engineers observed drivers rummaging around in their bags
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:51.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.76,English,,0,0,0,,or checking phones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.89,English,,0,0,0,,putting on makeup,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.98,English,,0,0,0,,or even sleeping in the driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.57,English,,0,0,0,,All these drivers were trusting the technology too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:06.17,English,,0,0,0,,which makes almost fully autonomous vehicles potentially more dangerous than regular cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:06.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.59,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, if the driver is distracted or not prepared to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:16.91,English,,0,0,0,,So this is why Waymo decided that the only safe way to proceed is with a car that has at least level four autonomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:16.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.33,English,,0,0,0,,This is the depot where the cars go when they're not on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.19,English,,0,0,0,,And it's also where people monitor all the rides in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.64,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes, so that's where my team sits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.75,English,,0,0,0,,You see three teams basically here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.51,English,,0,0,0,,One of the teams is my team of fleet dispatchers,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:39.22,English,,0,0,0,,so basically making sure that all the mission are assigned every day
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:39.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.31,English,,0,0,0,,and they are completed successfully on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.63,English,,0,0,0,,And then you have the Rider Support team that takes the calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:50.62,English,,0,0,0,,Thank you for calling the Waymo Rider Support. This is Beulah, how can I help today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:50.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:54.84,English,,0,0,0,,- I just completed my ride, but I don't wanna get out of the car. I just wanna keep driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:54.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.95,English,,0,0,0,,Is there a way that I can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:58.18,English,,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't see a trip started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:58.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.78,English,,0,0,0,,Give me one moment here while I partner with my team, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.27,English,,0,0,0,,- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.26,English,,0,0,0,,Well, I just left all my stuff in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.16,English,,0,0,0,,I hope it comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:24.35,English,,0,0,0,,- I think there's a lot of, still, resistance in terms of trusting the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:24.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:29.05,English,,0,0,0,,And they ask you like, "How does it feel to be in a car without the driver?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:29.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:35.31,English,,0,0,0,,I was the first person to do public roads, fully driverless ride at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:35.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.69,English,,0,0,0,,I always share the experience with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:42.16,English,,0,0,0,,It takes about two minutes for you to completely forget that you are in a driverless vehicle.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:42.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.92,English,,0,0,0,,If the system really provides that feeling that you're safe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.89,English,,0,0,0,,and you see a couple of maneuvers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:53.83,English,,0,0,0,,in less than two minutes, you're talking to whoever is next to you and not paying attention to what's happening anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:53.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.04,English,,0,0,0,,- Whoa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.22,English,,0,0,0,,it doesn't make the indicator sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.63,English,,0,0,0,,so I just don't know when it's going to turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.30,English,,0,0,0,,but if I was watching the map, I would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:13.86,English,,0,0,0,,I think we have this bias to believe that we're better at certain tasks than we actually are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:13.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.89,English,,0,0,0,,like thinking that people are good at driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:22.99,English,,0,0,0,,Surveys show 74% of people believe they are above average drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:22.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.50,English,,0,0,0,,Think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:28.55,English,,0,0,0,,In the 20th century, 60 million people were killed on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:28.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.77,English,,0,0,0,,That's basically an extra world war's worth of deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.70,English,,0,0,0,,And we really have no one to blame but ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:41.04,English,,0,0,0,,The National Transportation and Safety Board has identified human error as the cause of 94% of accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:41.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:45.14,English,,0,0,0,,Most of these errors are impossible for a machine to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:45.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:51.25,English,,0,0,0,,Every year when people are backing out of driveways or parking spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:51.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.60,English,,0,0,0,,in the U.S, up to 200 people are killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.76,English,,0,0,0,,and it's frequently older people or children, the children of the drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:08:59.99,English,,0,0,0,,It's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:08:59.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.97,English,,0,0,0,,And it comes down to the fact that we don't have eyes in the back of our head,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.35,English,,0,0,0,,and even the backup cameras still have blind spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:13.25,English,,0,0,0,,But if you have a vehicle that has lidar, and radar, and 29 cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:13.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.40,English,,0,0,0,,you're just not going to hit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:21.06,English,,0,0,0,,Up here in the very prominent top, there is a 360 lidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:21.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.76,English,,0,0,0,,So it can see all around the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.95,English,,0,0,0,,It can see up to 300 meters away with a lidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:32.09,English,,0,0,0,,The way the lidar works is it shoots out invisible laser beams,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:32.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.04,English,,0,0,0,,scanning around millions of times a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.05,English,,0,0,0,,and then it detects the reflection,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.72,English,,0,0,0,,\Nand how long it takes to come back allows you to determine how far it is to that object.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.57,English,,0,0,0,,So what it's doing is like painting a 3D picture of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.99,English,,0,0,0,,There are 29 cameras around this vehicle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.50,English,,0,0,0,,which gives you full 360 vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.79,English,,0,0,0,,It gives you close range vision, what is right next to the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:01.09,English,,0,0,0,,and also long range vision, going out 500 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:01.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:05.61,English,,0,0,0,,This car could detect a stop sign or a pedestrian 500 meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:05.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.57,English,,0,0,0,,How many of us have eyesight that is that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.53,English,,0,0,0,,There is also a microphone up on top
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.65,English,,0,0,0,,to listen to what's happening in the environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:19.38,English,,0,0,0,,and if there are sirens, then the car will pull over to the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:19.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.26,English,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be able to respond to emergency vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:35.35,English,,0,0,0,,What I wanna see here is, how does it handle a parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:35.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:39.71,English,,0,0,0,,where there's people driving in unusual ways
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:39.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:42.21,English,,0,0,0,,and possibly pedestrians walking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:42.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:47.64,English,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:47.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.79,English,,0,0,0,,That was a sudden stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.73,English,,0,0,0,,The car made a pretty hard stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.58,English,,0,0,0,,I think it saw that guy with a cart coming up on a pedestrian crosswalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.68,English,,0,0,0,,And one of the interesting things that the vehicle is always doing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:00.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.11,English,,0,0,0,,is not only seeing where things are and where they're going,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:04.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.65,English,,0,0,0,,but also making predictions about where they're likely to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:07.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:12.24,English,,0,0,0,,So this car doesn't just have one potential future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:12.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:15.96,English,,0,0,0,,It's constantly imagining, "Well, he might cross at the crosswalk,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:15.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.17,English,,0,0,0,,or, "He might keep going," or, "He might turn left,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:22.16,English,,0,0,0,,and so it has to be prepared for all of those different options.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:22.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.08,English,,0,0,0,,And it even weights the options
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.10,English,,0,0,0,,of like how likely it thinks that he's gonna go on the crosswalk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.03,English,,0,0,0,,versus go straight versus turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:34.31,English,,0,0,0,,And you can see that with the thickness of the line in the little simulated graphic that they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:34.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:41.29,English,,0,0,0,,A few years back, I think a lot of people were talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:41.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:46.16,English,,0,0,0,,how autonomous vehicles have to figure out who to hit in case of an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:46.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.04,English,,0,0,0,,like do the pick the orphan or the nun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.63,English,,0,0,0,,Should the car hit the motorcyclist with the helmet on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.91,English,,0,0,0,,because his injuries might be less severe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.87,English,,0,0,0,,or should the car hit the motorcyclist who does not have a helmet on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.97,English,,0,0,0,,because he did not properly protect himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.80,English,,0,0,0,,If cars were programmed to hit the motorcyclist with the helmet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:05.47,English,,0,0,0,,that would mean that, in a way, it would become safer to ride without a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:05.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:11.70,English,,0,0,0,,But the reality is that 99% of accidents aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:11.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:16.85,English,,0,0,0,,Every year, around 1.3 million people are killed on the roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:16.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.17,English,,0,0,0,,almost all of them due to human error.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.25,English,,0,0,0,,If autonomous cars can reduce these fatalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.74,English,,0,0,0,,then the real moral dilemma is not getting them on the road sooner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.37,English,,0,0,0,,for fear we haven't worked out exactly how they'll react
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:32.11,English,,0,0,0,,to extremely unlikely hypothetical scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:32.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.33,English,,0,0,0,,I think humans are becoming worse drivers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.90,English,,0,0,0,,because we're just so prone to distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:44.24,English,,0,0,0,,Think about the main reasons why cars crash:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:44.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:49.74,English,,0,0,0,,because people are speeding, they're under the influence, they're distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:49.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:55.35,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, these sorts of problems, an autonomous vehicle would not have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:55.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.39,English,,0,0,0,,You don't get a distracted driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:02.09,English,,0,0,0,,The ultimate question, right, that everyone wants to know, that I want to know the answer to is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:02.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.80,English,,0,0,0,,as these vehicles stand, are they better than the average human?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.61,English,,0,0,0,,Not than the best human, but just like an average human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:12.38,English,,0,0,0,,Like replacing some random car on the street with one of these vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:12.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.83,English,,0,0,0,,does that make the road safer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.89,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:19.86,English,,0,0,0,,I think we would never launch a rider-only service
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:19.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:23.27,English,,0,0,0,,if we did not meet that base safety framework.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:23.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:31.30,English,,0,0,0,,- If that's true, it means like every vehicle that's not on the road is kind of a worse situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:31.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:31.96,English,,0,0,0,,do you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:31.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:35.29,English,,0,0,0,,- We are really working really hard to launch this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:35.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.41,English,,0,0,0,,in larger areas and new areas too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:42.38,English,,0,0,0,,but we need to have the experience to show the regulators why we believe it's safer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:42.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:50.12,English,,0,0,0,,and, for that, you need to be driving miles, a number of miles that you feel comfortable with, statistically speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:50.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:54.44,English,,0,0,0,,- These vehicles have way more experience than any human driver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:54.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:14:00.22,English,,0,0,0,,because they've now accumulated data over 20 million miles of driving on public roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:14:00.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:07.09,English,,0,0,0,,If you were an average driver, you'd have to drive for a thousand years to accumulate that sort of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:07.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.88,English,,0,0,0,,And all of that experience can be used to train the systems, to fix the software,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.29,English,,0,0,0,,and used across all the vehicles in the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.90,English,,0,0,0,,In 2019, Waymo released a study of its data,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:24.26,English,,0,0,0,,over 6.1 million miles of automated driving in the Phoenix, Arizona metropolitan area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:24.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.66,English,,0,0,0,,Of the 18 total accidents that occurred during the study,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.20,English,,0,0,0,,none were serious enough to expect significant injury or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.78,English,,0,0,0,,In Waymo's Safety Report,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:39.33,English,,0,0,0,,they found some types of accidents have been completely eliminated by this autonomous driving system,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:39.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.08,English,,0,0,0,,like the car doesn't go off the road
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.09,English,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't hit stationary objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:47.05,English,,0,0,0,,Humans, humans do those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:47.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:52.70,English,,0,0,0,,If you look at the eight significant accidents that happened with Waymo vehicles
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:52.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.42,English,,0,0,0,,over the six million miles of driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.90,English,,0,0,0,,all eight of them involve a human driver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.07,English,,0,0,0,,of another vehicle doing something stupid,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:03.40,English,,0,0,0,,\Nlike driving on the wrong side of the road
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:03.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.90,English,,0,0,0,,or running a red light
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.84,English,,0,0,0,,or going through a stop sign
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:10.59,English,,0,0,0,,or failing to yield or going 20 miles per hour over the speed limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:10.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:15.09,English,,0,0,0,,There were three incidents involving Waymo vehicles and pedestrians,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:15.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.74,English,,0,0,0,,but in all three, the Waymo vehicle was stationary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:24.79,English,,0,0,0,,and the pedestrian or cyclist/skateboarder ran into the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:24.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.29,English,,0,0,0,,Waymo also takes some of that real-world data
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.83,English,,0,0,0,,and they put it into simulations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.45,English,,0,0,0,,and they tweak it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:37.16,English,,0,0,0,,So they try adding like a bicyclist going fast or going slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:37.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.43,English,,0,0,0,,or they make the car turn faster or slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:44.88,English,,0,0,0,,So they change all these parameters and variables, and they see what the software will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:44.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:49.52,English,,0,0,0,,And they've trained the software on an additional 20 billion miles of driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:49.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.72,English,,0,0,0,,not on the road but in the simulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.09,English,,0,0,0,,so that's a thousand times more experience again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.35,English,,0,0,0,,The question for me is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.74,English,,0,0,0,,when is stepping inside an autonomous car
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.60,English,,0,0,0,,gonna feel the same as stepping inside an elevator?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:08.53,English,,0,0,0,,Because I think that time may be coming sooner than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:08.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.63,English,,0,0,0,,I like the idea of this technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.41,English,,0,0,0,,but, honestly, getting in the car, I wasn't quite sure how I would feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.97,English,,0,0,0,,I was a little bit uncertain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.20,English,,0,0,0,,but once I saw.. it just handles so confidently...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.67,English,,0,0,0,,Like driving is one of those things that I feel like you can't hide whether you're a good or bad driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:28.04,English,,0,0,0,,It's just like, "Oh, what's gonna happen when there's a parked car or a cyclist or a pedestrian,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:28.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:32.10,English,,0,0,0,,and it just sort of handles all those situations with such confidence and ease
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:32.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.50,English,,0,0,0,,that I think I stopped thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.92,English,,0,0,0,,- After they pass a couple of your mental tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.66,English,,0,0,0,,you're like, "I'm good. I think I can.. I'llbe okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.86,English,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, yeah, I felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:48.08,English,,0,0,0,,I think a lot of people miss the bigger implications of what is achievable once fully autonomous driving is commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:48.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:52.60,English,,0,0,0,,Riders with disabilities, seniors, and the blind can get around more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:52.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.31,English,,0,0,0,,Transportation will get cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:59.77,English,,0,0,0,,Think of all the wasted value in the cars that spend over 95% of their time parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:59.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.28,English,,0,0,0,,We can regain a bunch of time and feel happier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.73,English,,0,0,0,,because commuting and being stuck in traffic sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.82,English,,0,0,0,,We can reduce traffic because vehicles will have better awareness of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.91,English,,0,0,0,,You can imagine one day when all the cars are fully autonomous,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.53,English,,0,0,0,,they can execute a beautiful ballet driving together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:23.39,English,,0,0,0,,and when that time comes, we can eliminate parking lots and add green spaces to our cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:23.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.42,English,,0,0,0,,And, most importantly, widespread adoption of autonomous cars
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.96,English,,0,0,0,,could prevent tens of thousands of fatalities in the U.S. alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.08,English,,0,0,0,,When do you think that this will be a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.11,English,,0,0,0,,like, clearly it's coming, but when?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.04,English,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. If you're talking about big cities,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:40.70,English,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping the next five years will be really game changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:40.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.37,English,,0,0,0,,- I'm excited to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:45.15,English,,0,0,0,,- Me too, believe me. Believe me. I just don't want to commute to work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:45.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:48.69,English,,0,0,0,,I would love to sit in the backseat, do my work on the way there and on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:48.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.34,English,,0,0,0,,- Or do something fun, watch a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.29,English,,0,0,0,,- Or sleep, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,
